ok so today and yesterday...both completely rocked.
yesterday i ate so much and lunch was great, it was subway. then today i got lots of school stuff to be happy about. 1) 102.7% in APUS! 2) 96 on bio test. 3) internship application! 4) invited to go to europe to earn school credit. 5)student of the month for science? i did not ever expect that one.

ive been promised a car...thats exciting too
only thing that sucked about today was mom wouldnt let me go to the movies with leanne and jenny, so were going next thurs instead. itll be fun! now i actually have something to do tues, thurs, friday of next week! wednesday is still free someone find something we can do!
 this week will definitely be great, i plan on stay up late.

hmm well i guess i really should have friends with me when i go to the mall, based on what stephanie just told me....creepy

ok im done rambling

hm my last entry was...weird

nothings really happened since then. i hate calculus thats whats happend. oh and like loads of people found out who i like but i dont really care anymore. whatever happens happens. the homestaed thing is cancelled, i really did want to do that, it gave me something to do. i hate english. field trip monday! i cant wait for that. i get to drive to school too! tehn it off to sammys house to study. hmm i dont think im allowed to go to the mall like ever. i think ill try to get a day where like everyone whos offered to go (well at least one person has to go with me) with me will go and then ill ask my parents. its just SO HIGHLY DANGEROUS because of course i wont fight back when i get abducted??! i need to go somewhere i think im going crazy. if my parents keep doing this to me i will. it is not possible for me to stay at home. im not that kind of person. i need to get out but to do that i need someone to go with me. not an adult, they annoy me. i need like a friend to go with me. whatever itll happen eventually. cant wait till college.

ok im done for now

i havent been here in a while. i dont remember last time i updated. i love the snow. its snowed 3 times in the past week or so. i called drew to rub it in his face. that was fun. when i told him i didnt have the patience to talk anymore cause i was hyper, he asked if he could call the house. told him no, it felt great. what a retard. 
i think i like someone else now. not quite sure. whatever. 
i cant sleep well anymore but i dont really mind. i like laying in the dark. it gives me time to think. 
started playing my guitar last week. its been awesome i love it. great fun. good way to annoy my parents too. im sorta sick of them. i cant do anything. its not fun. wont let me go to the mall by myself, movies by myself. college will be great. lots of work but still something i love and there will be parties thrown in there. most people say they cant picture me at a party. to that i say: just wait.
ive been thinking lots about college. i dont know where i want to go. except that its away from here. maybe west, maybe south. not north. i really need to think more about it. itll come to me one day where i want to go. i hate decisions. 
why do i think so much about stuff thats far away? well i guess its not that far away but im already thinking about it. i dont like that.
im gonna end this now.
ill type more later, or not. maybe tomorrow
